    <stitle>Body Builder Electrical Data Book - SINGLE REDUCTION AXLES: SPICER S100-S, S105-S, S135-S, S150-S - SERVICE
        PROCEDURES - CLEANLINESS
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="clean" graphiccount="0">
        <title>CLEANLINESS</title>
        <para>Axle carrier subassemblies should be steam cleaned prior to removal from the vehicle.</para>
        <para>Dirt is abrasive and will cause premature wear of otherwise serviceable parts. Service personnel should
            use a wash tank for thorough cleaning of parts just prior to reassembly.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
